    • getStockData

      public String getStockData​(String tickerSymbol)
      Description copied from interface: APIInterface
      Contains the functionality of AlphaVantageDemo, and downloads the stock data for the stock with the given ticker symbol on the given date. Returns all the data as a String in csv format - lines separated by newline characters, and individual cells separated by commas.
      Specified by:
      getStockData in interface APIInterface
      Parameters:
      tickerSymbol - the ticker symbol of the stock
      Returns:
      stock data as a String in csv format

    • getTickerMatches

      public String getTickerMatches​(String query)
      Description copied from interface: APIInterface
      The user can look up ticker symbols that match the name of a company, or all ticker symbols that start with the inputted string. This method will query Alpha Vantage for a list of matching results. It will only include results whose type is "Equity" and whose region is "United States".
      Specified by:
      getTickerMatches in interface APIInterface
      Parameters:
      query - the partial or full name of a company or ticker symbol being looked up by the user
      Returns:
      data in csv format of the ticker symbol matches. The columns output by AlphaVantage are symbol, name, type, region, marketOpen, marketClose,timezone, currency, and matchScore.
